Install CopyToTheBox app for Linux desktop or laptop

1 In a file browser/ navigator find your downloads (Desktop or Downloads)
2 Right click the install.sh and click "run as a program"
3 After the install, you will get a notice, click ok to the notice
4 Check your icon tray (bottom right or bottom row usually) for a CopyTotheBox icon
5 Delete install.sh and README.md if you downloaded those
6 You can uninstall by opening the app
7 You will find a log for the uninstall report on your desktop